            <title>[LU-1729] DLUBUF macro does not compile</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1729</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;in lustre/include/lu_object.h&lt;br/&gt;
#define DLUBUF &quot;(%p %z)&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
should be&lt;br/&gt;
#define DLUBUF &quot;(%p %zu)&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also LU_BUF_NULL is not always used when a lu_buf needs to be cleared&lt;/p&gt;</description>
